#. (itstool) path: component/name
#: org.kde.rsibreak.appdata.xml:6
msgid "RSI Break"
msgstr "RSI Break"

#. (itstool) path: component/summary
#: org.kde.rsibreak.appdata.xml:7
msgid "Helps prevent Repetitive Strain Injury by reminding you to take a break"
msgstr ""
"Esfortzu errepikakorrengatiko lesioa saihesten laguntzen du, atseden "
"hardezazun gogoraraziz"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.rsibreak.appdata.xml:9
msgid ""
"Prolonged use of a mouse and keyboard can cause a repetitive strain injury "
"(RSI), so computer users are advised to take regular breaks."
msgstr ""
"Sagua eta teklatua luzaroan erabiltzeak esfortzu errepikakorragatiko lesioa "
"(RSI «repetitive strain injury») eragin dezake, horregatik, ordenagailuen "
"erabiltzaileei atsedenaldi erregularrak egitea gomendatzen zaie."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.rsibreak.appdata.xml:11
msgid ""
"RSIBreak helps prevent repetitive strain injuries by keeping track of usage "
"patterns and periodically informing users to take breaks. During break "
"periods, RSIBreak can either show an unobtrusive message, lock the screen "
"entirely, or present a slideshow."
msgstr ""
"RSIBreak-ek esfortzu errepikakorragatiko lesioa saihesten laguntzen du, "
"erabilera-ereduen jarraipena eginez eta erabiltzaileei aldian-aldian atseden "
"hartzeko informazioa emanez. Etenaldietan, RSIBreak-ek mezu ez-oztopatzaile "
"bat erakusten du, pantaila erabat giltzatzen du, edo diapositiba emanaldi "
"bat aurkezten du."

